title: My Cafe by Ani Boland
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe on 2 floors, situated on the main street in Varna. Vegan choices include a salad of mixed veggies, the raw spinach cream soup served with wholegrain cracker, a tortilla sandwich with vegetables, quinoa, and vegan yogurt dressing; banana pancakes with a choice of toppings; and a couple other dessert options. Owner specializes in making bakery foods and teaches baking classes.
